Package org.swisscheese.swisscheese.texturePacks

This package contains classes relating to texture-packs used in the game.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TexturePack
    A texture pack object that contains WallTextures to be used in game.
    TexturePackList
    A list of TexturePack objects that are available for the user to select.
